Title: Complete
Description: The contract was concluded and in force, and is terminated due to its successful completion.

Title: Incomplete
Description: The contract was concluded and in force, and is terminated early due to some non-completion.

Title: Cancelled
Description: The contracting process was cancelled by the buyer or the procuring entity (for example, because of a change in needs, insufficient funds, or technical or procedural errors) after the award was made and the standstill period, if any, had ended.

Title: Unsuccessful
Description: The contract failed (for example, the winning bidder(s) refused to sign the contract) after the award was made and the standstill period, if any, had ended, but before the contract was concluded and in force.
